    "body": "<!-- .github/pull_request_template.md -->\r\n\r\n## 📌 Description\r\nAdd  filelock to `ensure_symlink`.\r\n\r\nPreviously hitting issues on v0.6.7.post1\r\n```\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]   File \"/vllm/vllm/model_executor/layers/fused_moe/experts/trtllm_fp8_moe.py\", line 351, in _apply_block_scale\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]     return flashinfer.fused_moe.trtllm_fp8_block_scale_moe(\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]            ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]   File \"/vllm/.venv/lib/python3.12/site-packages/flashinfer/fused_moe/core.py\", line 2461, in trtllm_fp8_block_scale_moe\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]     result = get_trtllm_moe_sm100_module().trtllm_fp8_block_scale_moe(\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]              ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]   File \"/vllm/.venv/lib/python3.12/site-packages/flashinfer/fused_moe/core.py\", line 814, in get_trtllm_moe_sm100_module\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]     module = gen_trtllm_gen_fused_moe_sm100_module()\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]              ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]   File \"/vllm/.venv/lib/python3.12/site-packages/flashinfer/jit/fused_moe.py\", line 273, in gen_trtllm_gen_fused_moe_sm100_module\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]     ensure_symlink(symlink_path, jit_env.FLASHINFER_CUBIN_DIR / bmm_export_path)\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]   File \"/vllm/.venv/lib/python3.12/site-packages/flashinfer/jit/cubin_loader.py\", line 251, in ensure_symlink\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]     shutil.rmtree(link)\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]   File \"/usr/lib/python3.12/shutil.py\", line 785, in rmtree\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]     _rmtree_safe_fd(fd, path, onexc)\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]   File \"/usr/lib/python3.12/shutil.py\", line 686, in _rmtree_safe_fd\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]     _rmtree_safe_fd(dirfd, fullname, onexc)\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]   File \"/usr/lib/python3.12/shutil.py\", line 686, in _rmtree_safe_fd\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]     _rmtree_safe_fd(dirfd, fullname, onexc)\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]   File \"/usr/lib/python3.12/shutil.py\", line 717, in _rmtree_safe_fd\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]     onexc(os.unlink, fullname, err)\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]   File \"/usr/lib/python3.12/shutil.py\", line 715, in _rmtree_safe_fd\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963]     os.unlink(entry.name, dir_fd=topfd)\r\n [multiproc_executor.py:963] FileNotFoundError: [Errno 2] No such file or directory: 'MmaDecl.h'\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 🔍 Related Issues\r\n\r\n<!-- Link any related issues here -->\r\n\r\n## 🚀 Pull Request Checklist\r\n\r\nThank you for contributing to FlashInfer! Before we review your pull request, please make sure the following items are complete.\r\n\r\n### ✅ Pre-commit Checks\r\n\r\n- [ ] I have installed `pre-commit` by running `pip install pre-commit` (or used your preferred method).\r\n- [ ] I have installed the hooks with `pre-commit install`.\r\n- [ ] I have run the hooks manually with `pre-commit run --all-files` and fixed any reported issues.\r\n\r\n> If you are unsure about how to set up `pre-commit`, see [the pre-commit documentation](https://pre-commit.com/).\r\n\r\n## 🧪 Tests\r\n\r\n- [ ] Tests have been added or updated as needed.\r\n- [ ] All tests are passing (`unittest`, etc.).\r\n\r\n## Reviewer Notes\r\n\r\n<!-- Optional: anything you'd like reviewers to focus on, concerns, etc. -->\r\n\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **Bug Fixes**\n  * Serialized symlink creation/update across processes to prevent race conditions during concurrent startup/initialization, reducing intermittent failures and timeouts.\n\n* **Tests**\n  * Added an end-to-end concurrency test that reproduces symlink race conditions across multiple worker processes and validates robust artifact generation and symlink integrity.\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
